<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">These&nbsp;days,&nbsp;I&nbsp;often&nbsp;ask&nbsp;myself&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;reporter&nbsp;why&nbsp;Foundation&nbsp;personnel&nbsp;behave&nbsp;the&nbsp;way&nbsp;they&nbsp;do.</a></div>
